Package: forgeKI
Title: Biology-First Knock-In Design and Repair-Pathway Donor Construction
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Dylan", "Conklin", email = "dubleeteam@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: Provides a reproducible, staged knock-in design workflow for
    HDR and MMEJ/PITCh reporter tagging. The package includes configuration
    and resource validation, exact hg38-aware guide and donor construction,
    optional crisprVerse guide-evidence audits, biology-first Type IIS
    domestication, HDR and MMEJ order-form generation, stable report-model
    exports, target-biology review, and Stage 10 cell-line context integration.
